title: Mutton Biryani-1
description: A hearty mutton biryani that will impress your guests instantly. Biryani is a dish that nobody can ever resist. Be it a dinner party or any celebratory occasion, biryani seems to be an ideal main dish to serve along with a spicy salan or refreshing raita.This mutton biryani recipe has layers of mutton and saffron-milk infused rice cooked 'dum' style. It has a host of aromatic spices and herbs such as star anise, bay leaves, cardamom, cinnamon, cloves, jaiphal, and javitri along with chillies, rose water, kewda and saffron cooked with succulent mutton pieces.
